.sp
pcocc console [OPTIONS] [VM]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
Connect to a VM console.
.sp
\fBNOTE:\fP
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
In order to leave the interactive console, hit CTRL+C three times.
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
